quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"Ṣãd. By the Quran, full of reminders"
  38,2,"˹This is the truth,˺ yet the disbelievers are ˹entrenched˺ in arrogance and opposition"
  38,3,"˹Imagine˺ how many peoples We destroyed before them, and they cried out when it was too late to escape"
  38,4,"Now, the pagans are astonished that a warner has come to them from among themselves. And the disbelievers say, “This is a magician, a total liar"
  38,5,"Has he reduced ˹all˺ the gods to One God? Indeed, this is something totally astonishing.”"
  38,6,"The chiefs among them went forth saying, “Carry on, and stand firm in devotion to your gods. Certainly this is just a scheme ˹for power˺"
  38,7,We have never heard of this in the previous faith. This is nothing but a fabrication
  38,8,"Has the Reminder been revealed ˹only˺ to him out of ˹all of˺ us?” In fact, they are ˹only˺ in doubt of My ˹revealed˺ Reminder. In fact, ˹they do so because˺ they have not yet tasted My punishment"
  38,9,"Or ˹is it because˺ they possess the treasuries of the mercy of your Lord—the Almighty, the Giver ˹of all bounties˺"
  38,10,"Or ˹is it because˺ the kingdom of the heavens and the earth and everything in between belongs to them? Let them then climb their way ˹to heaven, if their claim is true˺"
  38,11,This is just another ˹enemy˺ force bound for defeat out there
  38,12,"Before them, the people of Noah denied ˹the truth˺, as did ’Âd, Pharaoh of the mighty structures"
  38,13,"Thamûd, the people of Lot, and the residents of the Forest. These were ˹all˺ enemy forces"
  38,14,"Each rejected their messenger, so My punishment was justified"
  38,15,These ˹pagans˺ are awaiting nothing but a single Blast that cannot be stopped
  38,16,"They say ˹mockingly˺, “Our Lord! Hasten for us our share ˹of the punishment˺ before the Day of Reckoning.”"